.cs 7 on
.item 'WAIT Command' 'Added on 10/10/84 by LSO'
.boxon
WAIT nnnnn.nnn
.boxoff

.* DESCRIPTION
Required Privileges:  NONE (Internal use only)

* This command has not been released since there are still problems.

The WAIT command pauses the specified number of seconds before executing the
next command.

.* SELECT 'WAIT Command Options'
.us Option Descriptions

.* OPTION nnnnn
.ix 'nnnnn.nnn on WAIT Command'
nnnnn.nnn\\\\\\\specifies the number of seconds, 0.001 to 86400 (one day), to
                wait before executing the next command.  Pressing the BREAK
                key will terminate the waiting.
.cs 7 off
